    | |                  |   |
    | |                 | |  |
    | |        |     |  | |  |
     |   |    | |   | |  |  _|
        | |   | |   | |
         |     |     |
(Buyers take control)

Example for Bearish (Red Candlestick):

       |             |      _
      | |       |   | |  |   |
       |   |   | |   |  | |  |
   |      | |  | |      | |  |
  | |      |    |       | |  |
  | |                    |  _|
  | |
   |
(Sellers take control)
'''
